Package ch.pschatzmann.scad4j.d3

Class Cylinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.scad4j.SCAD4JObject
      • ch.pschatzmann.scad4j.d3.Cylinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICircleCommon, ISCAD, java.io.Serializable
    public class Cylinder
extends SCAD4JObject
implements ICircleCommon
    Creates a cylinder or cone centered about the z axis. When center is true, it is also centered vertically along the z axis. Parameter names are optional if given in the order shown here. If a parameter is named, all following parameters must also be named.
    Author:
    pschatzmann
